<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5782811">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5782811/" class="title-link">忍了好久</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5782811"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3034858/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3034858-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3034858/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">饮野客</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-02-18"
      class="main-meta">2013-02-18 18:43:22</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5782811_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                       早就想买这套书，忍了好久，终于在初七这天下决心订了一套，今天初九，快递员送来，拿走840块，留下了十本厚厚的书。到手后匆匆浏览一遍，感觉这套书从装帧到内容，整体上还是很不错的，值得细细阅读。书上标的是“第一辑”，不过估计第二辑是没什么希望出版了。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5782811/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5782811_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5782811_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










